(102, 1, '2013-03-29 16:07:00', '2013-03-29 20:07:00', 'Our mission is to Spread the Jam, which means introducing people all over the world to the skills and thrills of disc freestyle. The FPA is also the governing body for the judging system used at major disc freestyle tournaments. You can help us by becoming a member of our volunteer-run nonprofit 501(c)(3) organization. We currently offer three renewable levels of annual membership:<a href="http://freestyledisc.org/join.html#jammer">Jammer</a>,<a href="http://freestyledisc.org/join.html#competitor">Competitor</a>, and<a href="http://freestyledisc.org/join.html#platinum">Platinum</a>.', 'Join', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-autosave', '', '', '2013-03-29 16:07:00', '2013-03-29 20:07:00', '', 23, 'http://fpa.dev:8888/2013/03/01/23-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
