(241, 1, '2013-03-26 14:03:52', '2013-03-26 21:03:52', '<h3>Join today!</h3>\r\nEach annual membership includes 2 tournament quality freestyle discs (made possible by the generous support ofDiscraft and Discovering The World), a DVD featuring some of the greatest (and crustiest) jammers of our sport, and a Whiz Ring (which is like a fun training wheel for basic skills like air brushing).\r\n\r\nMembership discs are imprinted with the winner of the FPA disc design contest (see recent winning image). To get advanced news about how to submit a design for the next competition,<a href="http://freestyledisc.org/contact_us.jsp?toEmail=info">please send us a note</a>.\r\n\r\n[gravityform id="2" name="Join FPA" title="false" description="false"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[subscriptionform]', 'Join', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-12', '', '', '2013-03-26 14:03:52', '2013-03-26 21:03:52', '', 23, 'http://fpa.dev:8888/2013/03/26/23-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
